NG0271:1: ma ha amr-i ta tsakra dz+wa la tan+t+ra na ma /
NG0271:3: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud ces bya ba /
NG0271:4: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0271:5: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NG0271:6: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po chen po /
NG0271:7: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mnga' bdag chen po de ni /
NG0271:8: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i klong chen po
NG0271:9: 'og min gyi gnas ma bkod par snang ba zhes
NG0271:10: bya bar / 'di ltar sa bcu pa'i dus gsum
NG0271:11: gyi rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po rnams dang
NG0271:12: bya bar / */ lus kyi khams dgu 'dus pa'i
NG0271:13: dngas ma bdud rtsi chen po ye nas sangs rgyas
NG0271:14: pa'i don la so so ma yin tha mi dad
NG0271:15: cing dbyer med par bzhugs so //
NG0271:16: de nas rdo rje snying po rang gi gdan las bzhengs nas /
NG0271:17: seng ge'i 'gro stangs kyis bcom ldan 'das dpal kunatu bzang po'i spyan sngar mchis nas /
NG0271:18: glang po che'i lta stangs kyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi mes chen po'i zhal du bltas te //
NG0271:19: chos thams cad nam mkha'i rang bzhin can las dran
NG0271:20: pa sna tshogs nam mkha'i sprin bzhin du snang bar
NG0271:21: yang mkhyen nas chos nyid skye ba med cing 'gag
NG0271:22: pa med par shar ba'i phyir /
NG0271:23: bdud rtsi chen po rnam par rtog pa'i blo las
NG0271:24: rab tu 'das pa'i don 'di zhu bar mdzad pa'i
NG0271:25: phyir / 'di skad ces gsol ba 'debs so //
NG0271:26: kye ma ho chos sku nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NG0271:27: 'khor ba sprin gyis rab bsgribs pas //
NG0271:30: bla ma'i thugs kyi dpal be'u nas //
NG0271:31: man ngag sgron me dran med shar //
NG0271:32: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don //
NG0271:33: bdud rtsi chen po chos kyi sku //
NG0271:34: rnam rtog blo las rab 'das pa //
NG0271:35: skal ngan sems can 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0271:37: rnam dag sa thob drang srong dang *//
NG0271:39: don du bdud rtsi sgrub pa yi //
NG0271:40: dam chos 'khor lo bskor du gsol //
NG0271:41: zhes gsol ba rab tu btab bo //
NG0271:42: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po
NG0271:43: chen po chos kyi sku dri ma med pa'i dgongs
NG0271:45: sku yid bzhin du 'byung ba'i nor bu rin po che 'bar ba lta bus //
NG0271:46: 'khor gyi tshogs thams cad la rab tu gzigs nas /
NG0271:48: khams gsum 'khor bar sdug bsngal dug chen la //
NG0271:49: mya ngan 'das pa bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar bas //
NG0271:50: don dam kun bzang dbyer med lhun grub chos //
NG0271:51: rigs drug sems can kun la rang gnas pa //
NG0271:52: lus khams bdud rtsi chen po mchog gi chos //
NG0271:53: gsang ba bas kyang tshes gsang rab tu gsang *//
NG0271:54: yang gsang rmad byung chos kyi sgrub pa 'di //
NG0271:55: dran pa rnam rtog sems nyid tshogs brgyad la //
NG0271:56: dran med lus khams bdud rtsi sman sbyar nas //
NG0271:57: yi dam lha sku'i bdud rtsi skye ba med //
NG0271:58: zhen snang 'khor ba'i blo las rab 'das nas //
NG0271:59: mchog dang thun mong sgrub pa kun gyi gzhi //
NG0271:60: rmad byung bdud rtsi chos kyi 'khor lo 'di //
NG0271:61: khyed rnams tshogs la rab tu bskor bya yi //
NG0271:62: dad pa'i theg pas rdo rje bla ma zung *//
NG0271:63: brtson 'grus la gor skyen pos sman rnams btsal //
NG0271:64: shes rab mig rnon man ngag mthong bar bya //
NG0271:65: las dang skal bar ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NG0271:66: dpa' bo dpa' mo mched dang lcam dral la //
NG0271:67: phyi rabs don du bshad kyis legs par nyon //
NG0271:69: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NG0271:70: gling gzhi dang gleng bslang pa'i le'u ste dang po'o
NG0271:71: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bsgrub pa'i
NG0271:72: gzhi phun sum tshogs pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0271:73: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba dang *//
NG0271:74: gsang chen rab gsang de kho na //
NG0271:75: sgrub pa kun gyi gzhi yin pas //
NG0271:76: ston 'khor gnas dus sgrub pa'i rdzas //
NG0271:77: ston pa chos kyi mdzod 'dzin pa // rgyud lung man ngag rab shes bya //
NG0271:78: rgyu 'bras theg pa kun la mkhas //
NG0271:79: mngon du byung dang rna bar brgyud //
NG0271:80: thugs la brnag pa kho 'dug pa //
NG0271:81: zab dang rgya che'i dgongs pa rnams //
NG0271:82: ma lus lus pa med pa'i chos //
NG0271:83: theg pa rab rgyas yongs shes bya //
NG0271:84: thun mong khyad par 'khor ldan pa'i //
NG0271:85: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NG0271:86: 'dod yon lnga spang ma yin dang *//
NG0271:87: kri ya u pa yo ga dang *//
NG0271:88: bdud rtsi dka' thub spang ba yin //
NG0271:89: rgyal thebs ging dang las mkhan dang *//
NG0271:92: bung ba dug sbrul ltar gnas pa //
NG0271:93: rab tu dad pas bsgrub pa nyid //
NG0271:94: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung *//
NG0271:95: jo mos skyong la bran ltar las //
NG0271:96: gzungs ma rab tu ldan pa yang *//
NG0271:97: 'khor gyi dam par rab gsungs pas //
NG0271:99: dang por bsgrub pa'i gnas btsal ba //
NG0271:100: bdud rtsi dam pa bsgrub pa'i gnas //
NG0271:101: gtsang zhing gzhol ba drang srong gnas //
NG0271:102: dur khrod ma mo mkha' 'gro'i gnas //
NG0271:103: rtsi sman nags tshal sman gyis gsungs //
NG0271:104: khro bo srin po rab gnas yul //
NG0271:105: chu bo'i ngogs sam brag phug gam //
NG0271:106: rab tu dben par gnas pa yang *//
NG0271:107: brtag dang bslang dang gzung ba dang *//
NG0271:108: rin bcal ba dang bskrad pa dang *//
NG0271:109: sbyang dang bskor zhing byin gyis brlab //
NG0271:110: dgon par brtsigs sam dkyil 'khor bya //
NG0271:111: ston nam dpyid sos sman btsal bya //
NG0271:112: yang na dus ni bzhi po la //
NG0271:113: rtsa ba lo ma me tog gsum //
NG0271:114: 'bras bu bzhi yang btsal bar bya //
NG0271:115: bsgrub pa bya ba'i dus shis pa //
NG0271:116: tshes brgyad dag la 'du bar bya //
NG0271:117: nang du dkyil 'khor bri ba yang *//
NG0271:118: gang yin snga dro'i dus na shis //
NG0271:119: bsgrub pa gdon par bya ba yang *//
NG0271:120: bco lnga dag la rab tu tshar //
NG0271:121: dngos grub blang bar bya ba yang *//
NG0271:122: tho rangs sam ni nyi ma byed //
NG0271:125: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad kyang *//
NG0271:126: nyis ldab sum ldab dag tu bya //
NG0271:127: cha gsum dag tu rab gnas pa //
NG0271:128: dang po dkon mchog 'phags pa mchod //
NG0271:129: bar du tshogs kyi 'khor lo bya //
NG0271:130: tha ma gtang rag sbyin par dgye //
NG0271:131: bar chad rkyen yang rab bzlog phyir //
NG0271:132: go mtshon mda' gzhur rab bsags te //
NG0271:133: yungs kar dang ni gu gul gyis //
NG0271:134: bgegs rnams 'bros par byed pa dang *//
NG0271:135: nad khams gang la yod 'gyur ba //
NG0271:136: sman dang dpyad kyang rab ldan pa //
NG0271:137: mchod rdzas mchod pa rnam lnga dang *//
NG0271:138: rdzas brgyad rin chen sna bdun nyid //
NG0271:139: gtor ma rak+ta bdud rtsi dang *//
NG0271:140: rol mo rnga gling dung dang bcas //
NG0271:141: me long mda' dang tshon skud dang *//
NG0271:142: rgyal mtshan bla bre gdugs dang bcas //
NG0271:144: na li ke ra a ga ru //
NG0271:145: ga pur cu gang a ru ra //
NG0271:146: dza ti tsan+dan dmar po dang *//
NG0271:147: gur gum la stsogs tshang bar byed //
NG0271:148: yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni //
NG0271:150: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin pas //
NG0271:151: ston pa'i dam par rab rtogs bya //
NG0271:152: nyon mongs lnga ni rigs lnga nyid //
NG0271:153: che bas rab tu khengs pas na //
NG0271:154: nga rgyal chen po bdun dang ldan //
NG0271:155: rten 'brel bcu gnyis snang ba yang *//
NG0271:156: thabs mkhas rgyal sras sems dpar bshad //
NG0271:157: 'byung ba lnga nyid gzungs ma yum //
NG0271:158: rang lus dag pa'i zhing khams na //
NG0271:159: kun gzhi'i gnas chen chos kyi dbyings //
NG0271:160: lta bas chos rnam rtogs pa'i dus //
NG0271:164: dus chen 'di dang rab ldan bya //
NG0271:165: shes rab dang ni ting 'dzin nam //
NG0271:166: rnal 'byor pa yi sgrub rdzas yin //
NG0271:167: thabs kyi rdo rje chen po ni //
NG0271:168: gsang ba'i ston par rab tu shar //
NG0271:170: yab yum brda sprod thun mong 'khor //
NG0271:171: rdo rje pad+ma bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NG0271:172: gsang ba chen por rab gnas pa //
NG0271:173: sgron mar rab tu 'byongs pa'i dus //
NG0271:174: mtshan ldan gzungs ma rnyed dus nyid //
NG0271:175: kun rdzob byang sems dkar dmar rdzas //
NG0271:176: don dam bde ba bzhi dang ldan //
NG0271:177: gsang chen bstan pas lta ba rtogs //
NG0271:179: sgrol ging dag gis sgrol bar nus //
NG0271:180: spor ging dag gis spor bar nus //
NG0271:181: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NG0271:183: nang du gnas sbyang 'byongs pa dang *//
NG0271:184: zhing bcu gnas su khugs pa'i dus //
NG0271:185: mi dang glang po rta dang ni //
NG0271:186: bya khyi 'byong pa'i rdzas lnga ldan //
NG0271:187: rab gsang ston pa zhes bya ba //
NG0271:188: blta bas rab tu rtogs par byas //
NG0271:190: bying rgod gnyis las rab tu grol //
NG0271:191: spyod pa'i gnas la 'dug byas nas //
NG0271:192: mnyam gzhag rjes spyod 'brel bar shog / mchog dang thun mong 'bras bu ni //
NG0271:193: thob pa dus zhes bya ba yin //
NG0271:194: bla ma'i gdams ngag rdzas la spyod //
NG0271:196: de kho na nyid rab bshad bya //
NG0271:197: kun bzang bla ma tha dad med //
NG0271:198: yum dang kun tu bzang mo mnyam //
NG0271:199: rigs lnga bla ma'i 'khor du gcig / chos kyi dbyings dang 'og min gnas //
NG0271:200: bsgrub pa'i yul khams dbye ba med //
NG0271:201: 'di ltar gang shes dus kyi mchog / dus rnams nang nas khyad par che //
NG0271:203: kun bzang 'khor bar snang ba kun //
NG0271:204: don dam mya ngan 'das par sgrub //
NG0271:206: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las
NG0271:207: bsgrub pa'i gzhi phun sum tshogs pa bstan pa'i le'u
NG0271:208: ste gnyis pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das
NG0271:209: kyis sngon du bya ba'i rim pa 'di dag gsungs
NG0271:210: so // phyi nang bshags bskang mtshams bcad nas //
NG0271:211: dkyil 'khor byas la byin gyis brlab //
NG0271:212: chos kyi sbyin pa gtang ba'i phyir //
NG0271:213: shar du shes rab pha rol phyin //
NG0271:214: lho ru rgyas pa bkra shis byed //
NG0271:215: 'phags pa snang brgyad gdon par bya //
NG0271:216: bdud kyi bar chad zhi ba'i phyir //
NG0271:217: nub tu tog kyang bklag par bya //
NG0271:218: 'gyod tshangs bar gcod spa bkong zhing *//
NG0271:219: byang gi phyogs su gdon par bya //
NG0271:220: shes rab pha rol phyin ma'i sku //
NG0271:221: zhal gcig gser mdog seng ge'i khri //
NG0271:222: dang po chos 'chad mnyam par gzhag / tha ma rdo rje gleg bam 'dzin //
NG0271:223: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas sras dang bcas //
NG0271:224: nang du yang dag mchod par bya //
NG0271:227: rdo rje sems dpa' gtso bo gsum //
NG0271:228: sangs rgyas spyan dad ma ma ki //
NG0271:229: gos dkar mo ni yum du gnas //
NG0271:230: 'jam dbyangs spyan gzigs rdo rje can //
NG0271:231: bdag po gsum ni sras su 'khrungs //
NG0271:232: gshin rje gshed dang rta mgrin dpal //
NG0271:233: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa khro bo yis //
NG0271:234: rnon po rtse mo ki la ya //
NG0271:235: pho nya gsum dang rab ldan pas //
NG0271:236: dkon mchog gsum dang dpal mgon rnams //
NG0271:237: bgegs rigs 'gro drug la sogs pa //
NG0271:238: gtor ma mchod pas bskang bar bya'o //
NG0271:239: gnas dang nye ba'i gnas dang ni //
NG0271:240: zhing dang nye ba'i zhing gnas pa //
NG0271:242: dur khrod nye ba'i dur khrod sogs //
NG0271:243: ma mo mkha' 'gro lha srin rnams //
NG0271:244: rab tu bskang bar byas nas ni //
NG0271:245: tsha tsha gdab dang 'gyod tshangs dang *//
NG0271:246: srog chags tshe yang bskyab par bya //
NG0271:247: sku bzhi dpal brgyad tshang ba yi //
NG0271:248: shar phyogs su ni yul 'khor srung *//
NG0271:249: lhor ni rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NG0271:250: nub phyogs su ni spyan mi bzang *//
NG0271:251: byang ni rnas thos bu bkod nas //
NG0271:252: phyi mtshams tho yis gcad par bya //
NG0271:253: mi g.yo mgon pos dam sri gnan //
NG0271:254: phyi yi bar chad gshin rjes bsrung *//
NG0271:255: nang gi dngos grub 'phrog pa rnams //
NG0271:256: bdud rtsi 'khyil pas bsrung byas na //
NG0271:257: bar gyi mtshams yang gcad par bya //
NG0271:258: mi dge bcu po bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0271:259: phyogs skyong bcu la phur pa gdab //
NG0271:260: dug lnga'i mtshon chas kun 'joms phyir //
NG0271:261: mtshon cha 'bar ba'i dra ba dang *//
NG0271:262: ra ba gur gyis bsrung ba bya //
NG0271:263: lus ngag yid la bdag 'dzin pa'i //
NG0271:264: ru tra rnam pa gsum po yang *//
NG0271:265: blta spyod gnyis kyi mnan byas nas //
NG0271:266: sgo srung dur khrod bdag pos bya //
NG0271:267: de nas byin gyis rlobs pa yang *//
NG0271:268: dbang bskur chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0271:269: gnas khang byin gyis rlabs pa yang *//
NG0271:270: snod kyi 'jig rten khang pa na //
NG0271:271: bcud kyi sems can sna tshogs bzhugs //
NG0271:272: srid gsum bdud rtsi rnam lngar bsal //
NG0271:273: phyag rgya chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0271:274: rnal 'byor byin gyis rlabs par bya //
NG0271:275: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
NG0271:276: spyod lam rnam bzhi lha skur gsal //
NG0271:278: chad rlabs dza gad byin gyis brlab par bya //
NG0271:279: bsreg sbyang stong pa gzhal yas khang *//
NG0271:280: mi bskyod dbyings phyug 'od du zhu //
NG0271:281: ma ma ki yis bcud bsdus nas //
NG0271:282: cha gzhi dag tu 'go bar bya //
NG0271:283: yid bzhin nor bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0271:284: rdzas dang yo byad byin gyis brlab //
NG0271:285: yid bzhin nor bu rin po che //
NG0271:286: dpag bsam 'das pa'i shing chen dang *//
NG0271:288: ji ltar dmigs par 'byung bar snang *//
NG0271:289: sa yi lha mo brtan ma nyid //
NG0271:290: ser mo phyogs gnyis bum pa bsnams //
NG0271:291: phag gi khri la yang dag gnas //
NG0271:292: klu gnyan sa bdag 'khor dang bcas //
NG0271:293: de la sa ni rab bslang @#//
NG0271:295: bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chag chag gdab //
NG0271:296: ye shes dam tshig thig gdab la //
NG0271:297: ka ba brgyad dang 'khor lo brgyad //
NG0271:298: pad+ma brgyad dang rin chen brgyad //
NG0271:299: sgo bzhi rta babs brgyad ldan pa //
NG0271:300: rdul tshon byin gyis brlabs nas bri //
NG0271:301: de la lha yi sku yang dgod //
NG0271:303: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las //
NG0271:304: bsgrub pa'i sngon du 'gro ba'i las rim bstan pa'i
NG0271:305: le'u ste gsum pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan
NG0271:306: 'das kyis bsgrub par bya ba lha'i sku phyag rgya
NG0271:308: phyag rgya chen po lha yi sku //
NG0271:309: las kyi phyag rgya yum dang 'khril //
NG0271:310: dam tshig phyag rgya sbyor bar bya //
NG0271:311: chos kyi phyag rgya lha rnams bskyed //
NG0271:312: rang sems yi ge gsung du gsol //
NG0271:313: pha ma'i cha shas thugs mtshan nyid //
NG0271:314: 'byung chen lnga las sku rdzogs pas //
NG0271:315: cho ga rnam pa gsum las bskyed //
NG0271:316: rnam shes phung po rdo rje sems //
NG0271:317: g.yas mthing g.yon dmar dbus ma dkar //
NG0271:318: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NG0271:319: pad+ma ral gri dril bu bcas //
NG0271:320: gzugs ni snang mdzad gser gyi mdog / mthing ga dmar po'i dbu gsum pa //
NG0271:321: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen dang *//
NG0271:323: tshor ba dkon mchog dpal ni mthing *//
NG0271:324: dkar dang dmar ba phyag drug pa //
NG0271:325: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo dang *//
NG0271:328: dkar dang sngo dang bye ru'i mdog / pad+ma rdo rje 'khor lo dang *//
NG0271:329: dril bu rin chen ral gri bsnams //
NG0271:330: 'du byed don yon grub pa'i sku //
NG0271:331: dkar dmar ljang gu zhal gsum pa //
NG0271:332: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo dang *//
NG0271:333: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NG0271:334: dbyings phyug ma dang sangs rgyas spyan //
NG0271:335: ma ma ki dang gos dkar sgrol //
NG0271:336: rigs lnga bdud rtsi lngar gnas shing *//
NG0271:337: yum lngas sha lnga sbyong mdzad pa //
NG0271:338: khams dgu 'dus pa'i dngas ma nyid //
NG0271:339: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NG0271:340: sangs rgyas rigs ma yum dang 'khril //
NG0271:341: sa yi snying po sgeg mo dkar //
NG0271:342: rin chen smyu gu me long 'dzin //
NG0271:343: nam mkha'i snying po ma le mthing *//
NG0271:345: spyan ras gzigs dang klu ma dmar //
NG0271:347: phyag na rdo rje gar mkhan ljang *//
NG0271:348: rdo rje rtse lnga gar mdzad bsgyur //
NG0271:349: rnam shes bzhi dang yum bzhi yis //
NG0271:350: blo dang dngos po bsreg nas ni //
NG0271:351: byang chub sems dpa'i lha mo gnas //
NG0271:352: nang du yang dag spro ba'o //
NG0271:353: byams pa spos ma dkar mo la //
NG0271:354: klu shing 'dug spos ga pur bsnams //
NG0271:355: sgrib pa sel dang me tog mthing *//
NG0271:356: chos kyi 'khor lo me tog phreng *//
NG0271:357: kun bzang mar me dmar mo gsal //
NG0271:358: rin chen snye ma snang gsal 'bar //
NG0271:359: 'jam dpal dri chab ma ni ljang *//
NG0271:360: ut+pal dung phor dri chab mthing *//
NG0271:361: dbang po bzhi dang de yul bzhi //
NG0271:362: phyi yi snang ba dag dang @#//
NG0271:364: byang chub sems dpa'i rigs ma rnams //
NG0271:365: yul sems gnyis su med par byed //
NG0271:366: kun bzang yab yum mnyam bzhag mthing *//
NG0271:367: lha dbang brtson 'grus pi wang bsnams //
NG0271:368: lha min bsam gtan go cha dang *//
NG0271:369: mi dbang tshul khrims gseg par nyid //
NG0271:370: byol song shes rab po ti 'dzin //
NG0271:371: yi dwags sbyin pa rin chen sgrom //
NG0271:372: dmyal ba bzod pa me dang chu //
NG0271:373: gshin rje mi g.yo lcags kyu+u dkar //
NG0271:374: rnam rgyal rdo rje zhags pa ser //
NG0271:375: rta mgrin sbrul zhags lcags sgrog dmar //
NG0271:376: bdud rtsi rgya gram dril bu ljang *//
NG0271:377: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa la //
NG0271:378: rgyu yi dus nas dbang thob pas //
NG0271:379: bum pa mi bskyod chu yi dbang *//
NG0271:380: cod pan bdud rgyal rin 'byung la //
NG0271:381: rdo rje bdud 'joms snang mtha' yas //
NG0271:382: dril bu chos sgra don yon grub //
NG0271:383: ming ni rnam par snang mdzad do //

NG0271:514: mi snying rab tu sprul pa'i sngags so //
